data.description: Welcome to 2725 Melissa Ln, a charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom house for sale! This home is situated in a desirable neighborhood close to Dyess AFB, shopping, & restaurants. Inside you'll find a double sided brick wood burning fireplace, vaulted ceilings, & a split floor plan with an en suite bathroom in the primary bedroom. The HVAC system was recently replaced in 2022 & has been meticulously maintained just a little updating & some TLC to make it your own. With a 2 car garage & 1973 square feet of living space, this house has plenty of room for your & your family to enjoy. Don't miss out on this great opportunity. Schedule a viewing today!
